OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FActor Sir Idris Elba has received a
OL,7,Fknighthood from King Charles III.
OL,9,FHe was joined by 67 others, including
OL,10,Fcomedians Dame Meera Syal and Paul
OL,11,FElliott, one half of the double act
OL,12,FChuckle Brothers, who were also
OL,13,Fhonoured by the King.
OL,15,FLuther and Thor star Sir Idris was
OL,16,Fawarded a knighthood in the New Year
OL,17,FHonours for services to young people.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
