OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780589464
OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FIn 2022, the 53-year-old founded the
OL,7,FElba Hope Foundation, which supports
OL,8,Fcommunity empowerment, education,
OL,9,Fyouth advocacy and sustainable
OL,10,Fdevelopment.
OL,12,FSir Idris used a grant from the
OL,13,FPrince's Trust ` now the King's Trust
OL,14,F` to attend the National Youth Music
OL,15,FTheatre aged 18.
OL,17,FIt was announced last year that the
OL,18,Factor will team up with the King to
OL,19,Fcreate a documentary marking 50 years
OL,20,Fsince Charles founded the charity, due
OL,21,Fto air on Netflix this autumn.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
