OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780589464
OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FWatch: Sir Idris Elba is knighted by
OL,7,Fthe King
OL,9,FOlympic champions Dame Jayne Torvill
OL,10,Fand Sir Christopher Dean were also
OL,11,Fnamed in the New Year Honours list,
OL,12,Ffor services to ice skating and to
OL,13,Fvoluntary service.
OL,15,FThe ice dancers, who later became the
OL,16,Ffaces of celebrity competition show
OL,17,FDancing On Ice, took home the Olympic
OL,18,Fgold at the 1984 Winter Games for
OL,19,Ftheir "Bolero" performance.
