OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1780589464
OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FAfter finding out about the honour,
OL,7,FDame Jayne, 68, said the timing seemed
OL,8,F"perfect" after the two danced on the
OL,9,Fice for the final time last year.
OL,11,FShe said: "We had such a great time,
OL,12,Fwe were so happy with the tour and the
OL,13,Ffact that we got through it."
OL,15,FIt was a big thing for us to mark our
OL,16,Fcareer before retirement, and then
OL,17,Freceiving this award at the end of the
OL,18,Fyear, it's just finished everything.
OL,19,FIt's perfect."
