OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FThe Kumars At No 42 star Dame Meera
OL,7,FSyal, 64, will be recognised by the
OL,8,FKing for services to literature, drama
OL,9,Fand charity.
OL,11,FBorn in Wolverhampton, the actress had
OL,12,Fher breakthrough writing and starring
OL,13,Fin the BBC sketch show Goodness
OL,14,FGracious Me.
OL,16,FIn 2023 she was awarded the Bafta
OL,17,FFellowship, the academy's highest
OL,18,Faccolade for a career on screen.
