OL,3,CLuther star Sir Idris Elba knighted by
OL,4,Cthe King
OL,6,FRotherham comedian Paul Elliott, best
OL,7,Fknown as one of the Chuckle Brothers,
OL,8,Fwas made an Member of the Order of the
OL,9,FBritish Empire (MBE) for charitable
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FThe comedy double act, made up of Paul
OL,13,Fand his brother Barry, were a staple
OL,14,Fin British homes with their TV show
OL,15,FChuckleVision.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
